## 8. Call Chains

### 8.1 Upload a New File

```
User clicks Paperclip button
  → fileInputRef.current.click()
  → <input type="file" onChange={handleFileInputChange}>
  → for each file: uploadFile(file)

uploadFile(file)
  ├── [client] reject if MIME type not in ALLOWED_MIME_TYPES
  ├── [client] reject if file.size > 10 MB
  ├── setUploadingFiles([...prev, { id: tempId, uploading: true }])
  │
  ├── POST /api/attachments/signature
  │       { type: 13 (ChatFile), contentLength, contentType, baseId }
  │     ← { url, uploadMethod, token, requestHeaders }
  │
  ├── PUT <presigned MinIO URL>    ← binary, direct browser → MinIO (no backend)
  │
  ├── POST /api/attachments/notify/<token>   { filename }
  │     ← { path, size, mimetype }
  │
  └── POST /api/<baseId>/chat-files
            { token, name, size, mimetype, path }
          → ChatFileController.saveFile
          → ChatFileService.saveFile
              ├── [server] reject if MIME type not in ALLOWED_MIME_TYPES
              ├── [server] reject if size > 10 MB
              └── prisma.chatFile.create(...)
                  ← IChatFileVo
          → setUploadingFiles: mark entry { uploading: false, token }
          → refetchFiles()
```

### 8.2 Select Library Files

```
User clicks Files button (Popover trigger)
  → Popover opens

User checks a file's Checkbox
  → onCheckedChange → toggleFileSelection(file.id)
      → setSelectedFileIds (add or remove from Set)
  → selectedFiles recomputes via useMemo
  → chip appears/disappears above the input
