### 8.4 Delete a File

```
User clicks Trash icon on a file row in the Files tab
  → handleDeleteFile(fileId)
      → DELETE /api/<baseId>/chat-files/<fileId>

ChatFileController.deleteFile
  → ChatFileService.deleteFile(baseId, fileId)
